unique_equipment_enhance_rate.description: Hiyori's most prized belt.\nThe buckle, designed to resemble a ferocious beast, boosts its wearer's fighting spirit and lends greater strength to their blows.
Yui's most treasured hairband.\nDecorated with an intricate lace flower ornament, it inspires her to protect her friends no matter what.
A glove that Rei wears into battle.\nCombining offense and defense,\nit lends a sharpness to her strikes that allows them to penetrate any obstacle.
A handmade box of surprises that Misogi considers her greatest creation. Don't underestimate it as a mere kids' toy—its visual impact and explosive effects are enough to give any foe a mighty shock.
A medal that Matsuri was awarded by Nightmare. Just gazing at its glistening surface fills her heart with the flames of justice, stoking her resolve to strike down evil.
A three-pronged arcane spear imbued with all the force of Akari's love. Its powerful magical energy is enough to transform a little imp into a glamorous sorceress on the battlefield.

The ultimate pudding, huge in size and decorated with a meticulously selected variety of mouthwatering toppings. Even the living might find themselves drifting off to heaven after sampling a spoonful.
Yuki's favorite make-up compact. The radiant design further amplifies Yuki's brilliance, bringing humanity as a whole to their knees in awe of her cuteness.

Hecate of the Gale's unholy chain. Mere mortals would be reduced to empty shells the instant they touched its dark aura. The twilight glimmer of its blades beckons the unwary to the depths of Gehenna.
An ornately designed magical staff with some rather adorable touches. When swung to support one's allies with enchantments, it whips up a fairy-tale breeze carrying the Maho-Maho Kingdom's blessings.
An arrow enchanted with searing flames for Rino's use only.\nThe flames grow stronger in response to her passionate emotions, unleashing a deadly arc capable of ending an entire battle.
A one-of-a-kind ribbon that Shiori crafted as a present for her sister.\nIts shining star, instilled with pure affection, resonates with Hatsune's magical energy to extinguish the enemy's defenses.
The magical rod of a certain self-proclaimed magical girl. With a cybernetic flash (courtesy of its wielder's genius mind), it casts crazy OP spells that lay waste to enemies of love and justice!

One of Kasumi's indispensible tools of the detective trade, which she has used to solve countless puzzling cases. Never missing the tiniest of clues, it leads her without fail to the one true culprit.
The veil that Misato never goes anywhere without. Filled with the boundless love of its wearer, it heightens her allies' spirits and allows their attacks to strike where the enemy is weakest.

Suzuna's favorite brand of lipstick for special occasions. Its vivid red hue gives a refined yet sultry and bewitching impression, making it nigh impossible to tear one's eyes away from the lips it adorns.

A sacred scroll describing the most secret techniques of the Ryukyuan school of karate that Kaori follows. Thanks to a unique enchantment, its words are invisible until a true master's spirit illuminates them.
The whip that Io uses as a pointer in her lessons. No matter how dull the subject, any lesson taught by this teacher will surely be a delightful experience.
The sword Mimi takes wherever she goes. When she swings it around, happily entranced by its cute design, its surprisingly long reach keeps all nasties at bay.
The bell that Kurumi always carries as a protective charm. Though ornate in appearance, the delicate tones it produces have a reassuring familiarity that lends courage to its timid wielder.
An arcane throwing spear, tailored to channel Yori's magical energy. By drawing upon her vital force, it can reduce her surroundings to ash in a single fell sweep.
Ayane's trusty partner, now more powerful than ever before. The mighty strength he wields knocks Ayane's enemies senseless for extended periods of time.
A dress that embodies the spirit of a maid's services. Suzume's loyalty towards Saren exudes from the apron, boosting her magical power and lowering enemies' physical defense.
A pendant fitted with a legendary acorn possessing vast magical potency. Acting as a catalyst to enhance Rin's magic, it lends great strength to all allies around her.
This sacred axe converts the fierce intensity of Eriko's love directly into destructive force. With each passionate blow, its blade chimes a wild rhapsody of carnage.
Saren's favorite hair accessory, and an emblem of the strength within her kindness. When this tiny wing takes flight, the wearer's body is released from gravity itself.
A hand microphone custom made for Nozomi. Adorned with a sweet ribbon bearing the Carmina logo, it represents her aspirations to the height of stardom.
Ninon's trademark war fan.\nIts scarlet leaves raise gusts of air that burst into explosive flame, scorching a path through anything foolish enough to stand in her way.
Shinobu's professional garb, wreathed in blue spectral flames. Woven from special threads that channel spiritual energy, it calls upon departed souls to aid her.
A brooch that Akino displays with pride. Mounted with a gemstone passed down for generations in the House of Wisteria, it enhances the wearer's noble spirit.
Mahiru's poncho, designed to resemble her beloved cow Elizabeth. Sparks a flair for comic mishaps that will leave the enemy thoroughly perplexed.
Yukari's trusty tankard that she never goes anywhere without. Refills itself with an invigorating tonic that floods the drinker's body with boundless energy.
Kyoka's trusty magic staff. Topped by an orb imbued with the power of a high-ranking water dragon, it is said to change its form to suit the one who wields it.
A precious sword passed down for generations in the Mikuma school of swordsmanship. Forged to feel as light as a feather, in Tomo's capable hands, it sweeps enemies aside like a flurry of wind.
A one-of-a-kind amulet that Hatsune gave Shiori as a gift.\nA constant reminder of her sister's affection, it emboldens Shiori to call on her deepest strength.
The beret that Aoi wears wherever she goes. Decorated with a pair of feathers to symbolize powerful bonds, it serves to remind Aoi that she is never truly alone.
An elaborate book of sheet music recording Song Summoning spells of courage. Recited in Chika's dulcet tones, its melodies sharpen her allies' senses, allowing them to strike the enemy's weak points.
A mighty blade that houses the soul of an azure wolf. Awakening the latent instincts of its wielder, it assaults the enemy with a hurricane of ferocious strikes.
An axe that Illya has wielded through the centuries. Its mighty blade, surging with crimson magic, sucks the fresh blood from its victims as sustenance for its vampiric mistress.
A choker that doubles as one of Kuka's bondage goods. Enemies are enticed by the sight of her self-binding, arousing the primal pursuit of pleasure within them.
Tamaki's most treasured pendant. The magical gems embedded in the taiyaki design boost her agility, leaving enemies gaping at the afterimages she leaves behind.
Jun's sturdy suit of armor. Imbued with the blazing flames of justice, it repels all attacks without fail, inspiring Jun's allies to perform remarkable feats.
Mifuyu's faithful halberd. Each swing of its blade sends powerful currents dancing through the air, protecting the wielder from harm with their watery blessings.
The hallowed weapon that Shizuru calls her own. Enchanted with a protective charm, it resonates with the wielder's noble spirit to deliver her allies from harm.
Misaki's magic wand and partner, better known by its nickname "Ai." Though this living weapon has evolved to wield terrifying new power, its owner mostly uses it as a guinea pig for new makeup ideas.
Mitsuki's decorative eyepatch, featuring a bewitching floral design. When supplied with magical energy, it emits a rainbow glow that saps the enemy's life.
A gorgeous order-made dress that Lima longs to wear someday.\nThe power of a pure maiden's heartfelt dreams is not to be underestimated.
Monika's trademark coat. Its glorious design rouses the spirits of those who follow her lead, significantly boosting every aspect of their offensive capabilities.
The one-of-a-kind belt that Tsumugi uses to store her bobbins of thread. By quickly drawing and spinning these magical threads, she can rapidly tie up enemies, disabling them in an instant.
A hooded cloak that Ayumi made herself, designed to reduce her visibility. It allows her to get close to other people without being noticed... particularly a certain specific individual.

The two finely crafted katana that Ruka wears by her side. She rarely draws her second blade, Haromaru, in battle, but on those occasions when she does, hordes of villains have been known to fall in a flash.
A blade obtained by Djeeta as a means to perfect her technique. Those who cleave through a tormented world with a clear mind and sound technique are said to be heralded as true masters of the blade.
The true form of Pecorine's Royal Equipment. Though its abilities have always been potent, this newly unleashed power allows her to tap into a deeper strength.
Kokkoro's treasured hair ornament. Blessed by the divine entity she faithfully worships, its delicate fragrance renews her strength to face whatever challenges arise.
The spellbook from which Karyl draws her magic. By harnessing the torrent of magical energy within its pages, she can unleash mighty spells at will.
The longbow Arisa wields in battle. A legendary elven artifact, merely aiming it at a target is enough to halt their motion, and the arrows it fires can penetrate any obstacle.
Christina's deadly greatsword. Each swing's vector is perfectly calculated to ensure it cleaves its target without fail, guaranteeing absolute victory.
A combination sword and parasol that Pecorine prepared for a summer trip. If her beaming smile somehow isn't enough on its own, her cute and elegant sword skills will gather all eyes on the beach.
Kokkoro's spear, decked out for a summer occasion. Its refreshingly cool blade weaves ribbons of icy blue through the air, dispelling the summer heat as swiftly as it dispatches monstrous foes.
A new magic staff that Suzume prepared just for the sunny season. Its fancy decorations call to mind luxurious summer resorts, and the parfait remains intact no matter how many times she falls over.

The rubber ring that Karyl quietly purchased to ensure her summer would go swimmingly. She insists that she chose it for balance alone, but with such a cute design, some find her claims a little suspect.
An unusual ice pop that Tamaki uses to defend herself against the summer heat. Its fusion of ice and taiyaki puts a spring in her step, allowing her to dart with feline agility between enemy attacks.
This spear is Mifuyu's efficient solution to any troubles that might disturb her perfect summer. Producing waves that call to mind a great sea deity, it sweeps foes away beyond the horizon.

A Halloween gift that Shinobu received from her father. Imbued with the energies of this special night, its lantern guides wayward souls to the next life while its blade swiftly reaps less savory spirits.
A magnificent creation depicting a Halloween party in pudding form. Its delectable sweetness tinged with a subtle pumpkin flavor was enough to surprise even a pudding connoisseur like Miyako.

Misaki's living staff (better known as Ai), dressed up in a costume for Halloween. By its mistress's own estimation, the design is an ideal combination of "very grown-up violence" and "seasonal cuteness."
Chika's magical staff, blessed by the spirits of the holy season. Resonates with the spirits Chika summons to provide sacred wards that greatly boost their targets' abilities.
Kurumi's beloved bell, enchanted with seasonal blessings. With each earnest swing, it grants her allies the courage never to give in.
Ayane's trusty partner, dressed up for the festive season. Not only is he cuter than ever, he also boosts Ayane's abilities, allowing her to deal even more devastating blows.
A gauntlet passed down in a shrine dedicated to feline deities. Said to lead its wearer to victory, it resonates with Hiyori's pure heart to summon countless blessings.
A staff used at ceremonies welcoming the new year. When held high by one who wishes for the happiness of others, it produces a flurry of petals that herald a wonderful future.
A celebrated sword used in ceremonies greeting the new years' deities. With a blade as cold and elegant as ice, it severs the darkness of night and the curses of impure thoughts.
A cooking utensil prepared by Eriko to create chocolate for her soulmate, and beyond the ability of any but her to control. Capable of beating anything in its path into a creamy consistency.
The hat that Shizuru wears when making delicious chocolate for her beloved little brother. Its namesake heart accessory gives off a sweet aroma, filling her allies with the spirit of romance.
The spellbook Anne carries, giving her access to the full depths of her significant magical talents. Her royal resolve to lead a nation grants strength to the spirits she calls upon.
Lou's inseparable partner. The fact that he sticks by her even in a distant land, letting her treat him as a handy tool like always, is a testament to their deep bond... probably.
The amulet of a dragon, which heightens Grea's natural magical energy. Empowered by the blessings of its crystal, the dragoness's flames grow fierce enough to incinerate any foe.
An alluring kimono that makes Kuka's heartbeat race. Adjusting the tightness of the belt allows her to build up ecstasy, and when released, it sends her spinning away in a glorious climax.
The true ninja equipment that Ninon purchased in Oedo Town. The weapon itself doesn't appear to have any special power, but it somehow causes Ninon to awaken hidden ninja skills.
